column17: long-description:"Get early access to Battlefield V with Battlefield V Deluxe Edition and experience how war will never be the same. With exceptional outfits and assignments for the British Special Air Service and the German Airborne troops
column18: Battlefield V Deluxe Edition will make you stand out on the battlefield with five sets of paratrooper apparel containing weapon skins
column21:
and face paint.

• Early Access to Battlefield™ V Base Game
• Five Sets of Paratrooper Outfits
• Special Assignments and Starter Assignments – test your skills on the battlefield and gain rewards.
• 20 Weekly customization items with Airlift

Pre-Order Battlefield V Deluxe Edition for More Bonus Content Including:
• Early access to the Battlefield V Open Beta.
• 1 additional Special Soldier Set.
• Immediate Access to Five Battlefield 1 Weapons*.

Remote Play requires PS Vita system and sufficiently robust Wi-Fi connection.
